column2: "Oh, have you finished already? I should have expected no less from the Guardian."
"Hmm, are these the grapes you have gathered? I suppose I had better try one."
"Oho, what have we here... This dark, tense skin... And beneath it, the delicate but richly sweet flesh..."
"Oho, what have we here... This dark, tense skin... And beneath it, the delicate but richly sweet flesh..."
"These are superb. And you have procured more than enough for my experiments."
"You have my sincere gratitude, Guardian. I hope you will continue to lend my sister your aid."
